    UCI Procurement Services
   </h1>
   <section aria-labelledby="introduction-heading" class="section-banded" id="introduction">
    <div class="container">
     <h2 class="section-heading sr-only" id="introduction-heading">
      <span>
       Section 1
      </span>
     </h2>
     <div class="row">
      <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-4">
       <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
        <div class="bucket-image bucket-image-center">
         <img alt="Snehal Bhatt Chief Procurement Officer" src="SnehalBhatt.jpg"/>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-8">
       <div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
        <h3 class="widget-heading h3">
         <span>
          Procurement Services
         </span>
        </h3>
        <p>
         Procurement Services is your trusted strategic partner dedicated to providing the most effective and efficient customer service in support of UCI’s mission and goals. We strive to create an environment that enhances productivity while offering collaborative, innovative, and leading best practices in procurement for the acquisition of quality goods and services by implementing procurement processes and procedures that deliver high quality expertise, significant value, and excellent customer service.
        </p>
        <p>
         If you are a new employee (staff or faculty), please visit our
         <a href="training/training-resource.php">
          Training and Resources
         </a>
         or
         <a href="mailto:procurement@uci.edu">
          contact us
         </a>
         to further assist you.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Snehal Bhatt
         </strong>
         <br/>
         <strong>
          Chief Procurement Officer
         </strong>
         <br/>
         <strong>
          Procurement Services
         </strong>
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </section>
   <section aria-labelledby="section-2-heading" id="section-2">
    <div class="container">
     <h2 class="section-heading sr-only" id="section-2-heading">
      <span>
       Section 2
      </span>
     </h2>
     <div class="row">
      <div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-12">
