          <img alt=" Procurement Services" src="img/Cart_1_260579423.jpg"/>
         </a>
        </div>
        <p>
         Sourcing and Purchasing Services works to develop collaborative relationships with departments and suppliers, leverage the power of collective spend, and drive down total cost of ownership to support the redirection of savings to teaching, research and public services.
        </p>
        <p>
         <strong>
          Quick Links:
